@delahaya - The time before Christianity was not the Stone Age. Most scientists are not Christian's, though most scientists have been religious at times when most people had no real choice but to be religious as they would either be ostracized, executed or had no way of seeing outside their tiny box because their whole lives they had been taught by their schooling, by those they loved, by authority to believe in things that there was scant, if not no, evidence for. Many scientists suffered greatly trying to reconcile what they had been taught all their lives and what they could see in their research. Those were very sad and hard times but thankfully humanity is leaving organised religion behind and maybe we can all get a long a little better without all those absolute truths and dogmatism's.
I do not think TPB should remove this torrent, but we definitely need to keep a eye out for harmful propaganda in all it's forms and warn fellow users.
